{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"153e8fdbdc","title":"中央转发察哈尔省委关于进一步普及镇反宣传计划的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"2c17c5b564","index":0,"year":1951,"month":5,"day":16,"articleId":"153e8fdbdc"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-shzygz","name":"中国五十年代初中期的政治运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""},{"id":"maoquanji30","name":"毛泽东全集第30卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/30-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-shzygz":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"48ca602b8a","type":"title","text":"中央转发察哈尔省委关于进一步普及镇反宣传计划的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"153e8fdbdc"},{"id":"5f693262d6","type":"authors","text":"毛泽东","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"153e8fdbdc"},{"id":"19ca2e932d","type":"appellation","text":"各中央局，并转分局，省委，区党委，市委，地委，县委：","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"153e8fdbdc"},{"id":"98efc8a3de","type":"paragraph","text":"兹将察哈尔省委关于进一步普及镇压反革命宣传的计划发给你们。中央认为这个计划是完全正确和完全必要的，全国各地均照此计划去做。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"153e8fdbdc"},{"id":"55b5bbd326","type":"paragraph","text":" 中央五月十六日","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"153e8fdbdc"}],"page":{"id":"071698cc47","publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"153e8fdbdc","start":0,"end":0}},"maoquanji30":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"29c8e5d8ca","type":"title","text":"中央转发察哈尔省委关于进一步普及镇反宣传计划的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"153e8fdbdc"},{"id":"3c186fdb12","type":"paragraph","text":"[I]中共察哈尔省委这个计划的主要内容是：（一）各级党委宣传部将镇压反革命的宣传作为当前工作重心之一。（二）各区普遍召开一次各界代表会，各村普遍举行若干次各阶层的座谈会，专门讲解《惩治反革命条例》，联系本区、本村的镇压反革命工作，进行讨论，使群众明了政策。（三）大力组织群众学习《惩治反革命条例》和防好常识。（四）在镇压反革命的紧张阶段，应利用群众关心的每一个具体事件，经常向群众作报告。（五）各种对外宣传的报纸、刊物，均应发表专论。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"153e8fdbdc"},{"id":"5ebacc7209","type":"paragraph","text":"五月十六日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"153e8fdbdc"},{"id":"e3f1d86579","type":"paragraph","text":"各中央局，并转分局，省委，区党委，市委，地委，县委：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"153e8fdbdc"},{"id":"f4d27b0670","type":"paragraph","text":"兹将察哈尔省委关于进一步普及镇压反革命宣传的计划“发给你们。中央认为这个计划是完全正确和完全必要的，全国各地均照此计划去做。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"153e8fdbdc"},{"id":"f83101b44b","type":"subtitle","text":"中央","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"153e8fdbdc"}],"page":{"id":"afbf50ef2c","publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"153e8fdbdc","start":312,"end":312}}}},"__N_SSG":true}